- All right, look.

804
00:58:14,760 --> 00:58:17,354
If you feel that way,
just forget about it, okay?

805
00:58:17,440 --> 00:58:19,271
You haven't any claims on me, mister.

806
00:58:19,360 --> 00:58:20,918
